{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-page-template-js","path":"/pages/about/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"9f50a3aa-2556-5142-8805-7fd3bcdc5240","html":"<p>瑶子(Yoko) was born in Japan. She started drawing and programming when she was a child.</p>\n<p>Since graduating from an university, she’s been developing backbone systems of local governments and companies in the IT industry.</p>\n<p>Currently she is not only working as an engineer, but also producing watercolors as an artist. She produces her art by the beautiful scene that comes to her mind.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 900px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8875276233c51567ee9f1c3d10579128/2d017/aboutme.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/8875276233c51567ee9f1c3d10579128/01472/aboutme.webp 240w,\n/static/8875276233c51567ee9f1c3d10579128/222bd/aboutme.webp 480w,\n/static/8875276233c51567ee9f1c3d10579128/31462/aboutme.webp 900w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/8875276233c51567ee9f1c3d10579128/3bc27/aboutme.jpg 240w,\n/static/8875276233c51567ee9f1c3d10579128/98431/aboutme.jpg 480w,\n/static/8875276233c51567ee9f1c3d10579128/2d017/aboutme.jpg 900w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/8875276233c51567ee9f1c3d10579128/2d017/aboutme